  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, COU omitted)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research settings to evaluate hemolysis risk for centrifugal blood pumps under ventricular assist device operating conditions. CFD-based hemolysis predictions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump were assessed under MRL 5 requirements. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across 13 credibility factors; 7 factors were formally assessed and 6 were flagged as epistemic gaps. The credibility evidence compiled here supports regulatory submission review. No structured Context of Use object is provided under the Minimal profile; intended-use scope is described only in this narrative.",
